subSubSection.paragraph:
Pso formula 3,3/1,3,3/3,3,3,5,3 dorsally and 1,2/0,1,1/2 +1,1,1,1 ventrally; Abd I sternite with 1 +1 pso in anterior position, 1 + 1 pso at the base of the VT, and 1 + 1 lateral pso; Abd II–III only with the paired lateral pso; Abd IV only with the medial paired pso (
Figs 8, 9
). Each subcoxa 1 of legs I–III with 2 pso. Neither psx nor psp could be distinguished.

